I was hoping for a balanced mix of WW2 era military music. But instead I get this Nazi fanboy list of songs. 

I have only got about 30% of the songs and so far about 30% of these are various versions of 'die fahne Hoch' basically if you don't know, that's the main Nazi theme.

The rest is 90% SS battalion/corp songs. 

In short next to none of these songs are not German and hardly any are standard whermarcht most are SS/Nazi party racist crap.
